# Build-time embedded ffmpeg/ffprobe (scripts/build/fetch-embedded.sh output)
# Use **/ prefix so it matches both <root>/build/embedded/ and any accidental
# copies (e.g. src/build/embedded/ if a tool resolves cwd wrong).
**/build/embedded/